<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV55">
<l>maṉṉumāma larkkiḻatti vaiyamaṅkai maintaṉāyp</l>
<l>piṉṉumāyar piṉṉaitōḷma ṇampuṇarnta taṉṟiyu</l>
<l>muṉṉapāta meṉṉacintai maṉṉavaittu nalkiṉāy</l>
<l>poṉṉicū ḻaraṅkamēya puṇṭarīka ṉallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Becoming the husband of the Lady-love who abides on the great lotus and Lady Earth,</l>
<l>And besides uniting with the shoulders of Cowherdess Piṉṉai afterwards,</l>
<l>O You who bestowed grace by placing Your feet in my thoughts</l>
<l rend="indent">so that they last [forever]!</l>
<l>Aren’t You the [Lord] with lotus[-like eyes] who dwells in Raṅgam</l>
<l rend="indent">surrounded by the Poṉṉi?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
